1. *Motiv* je važan faktor za uspešan rad. (The motivation is an important factor for successful work.)
2. On je imao dobar *motiv* za svoje delo. (He had a good motive for his work.)
3. Ona je potaknuta *motivom* da uspe. (She was motivated by the motive to succeed.)
4. Njegov *motiv* je da obezbedi bolji život za svoju porodicu. (His motive is to provide a better life for his family.)
5. Oni su se podstakli *motivom* da postignu više. (They were spurred by the motive to achieve more.)